हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/k9KXgW
show.description: Desperate Husbend Revange is story of a devoted husband’s world collapses when he uncovers his wife’s ultimate betrayal. But heartbreak turns into a ruthless plan; each move calculated to destroy the trust, pride, and peace of those who wronged him. What begins as pain soon becomes a game of power, where revenge is the only victory.
